:plain
  ---
  layout: default
  title: index page
  ---
%header
  %h3 Hi!
  %hgroup
    %h1 Welcome
    %figure
      %img{src: "/assets/i/me.jpg"}
      %figcaption A smug looking...
    %h2 I love minimal, functional design and development techniques, typography and all things web.

%section#bio
  %p blablabla, oooo, blablabla...

%section#articles
  %header
    %h1
      %span An archive of articles
  %dl
    {% for post in site.posts %}
    {% unless post.next %}
    %dt {{ post.date | date: '%Y' }}
    {% else %}
    {% capture year %}{{ post.date | date: '%Y' }}{% endcapture %}
    {% capture nyear %}{{ post.next.date | date: '%Y' }}{% endcapture %}
    {% if year != nyear %}
    %dt {{ post.date | date: '%Y' }}
    {% endif %}
    {% endunless %}
    %dd
      %article
        %a{href: "{{ post.url }}"}
          %h1 {{ post.title }}
          %h2 {{ post.excerpt }}
    {% endfor %}